** What is Iago supposed to arrange for Roderigo? Do you think that Iago is really concerned with this or is he just using Roderigo?
   Iago is supposed to arrange their marriage because Roderigo loves Desdemona but she loves Othello instead. With his help, Iago claims that he will make them be together, all Roderigo has to do is to listen and follow his instructions. However, in reality, Iago couldn't care less about Roderigo. All he wants is vengeance and he will use any body to succeed, including poor Roderigo.

